title: Affascinante concept art ufficiale per Captain Marvel
body:
Affascinante concept art ufficiale per Captain Marvel

Andy Park, direttore dello sviluppo visivo e concept artist Marvel Studios, ha rilasciato – via Twitter – un nuovo concept art ufficiale relativo a Captain Marvel.

Il concept art di Andy Park è stato mostrato lo scorso anno, in occasione del panel Marvel del San Diego Comic-Con 2017.

Captain Marvel è diretto da Anna Boden e Ryan Fleck. La sceneggiatura è di Ginevra Robertson-Dworet e Nico…

summary: Captain Marvel Concept Art Officially Released!
title: Captain Marvel Concept Art Officially Released!
body:
#CaptainMarvel Concept Art Officially Released!

At Marvel’s 2017 San Diego Comic Con Hall H panel, they revealed the first look at Brie Larson as Captain Marvel in the form of a piece of concept art by Andy Park. While there have been blurry cellphone pictures of this piece being spread around the internet for months, they haven’t released an official version of the image…until now.

Today Andy Park Tweeted a nice high-res image of the concept…

summary: Marvel Comics Reboots Captain Marvel in Brand New #1
title: Marvel Comics Reboots Captain Marvel in Brand New #1
body:
Marvel Comics Reboots Captain Marvel in Brand New #1

Marvel Comics will once again be rebooting Captain Marvel with a brand new #1 issue in January.

The series will be written by Kelly Thompson with art by Carmen Carnero and colors by Tamra Bonvillain. The first issue will also feature a cover by long-time Harley Quinn scribe and artist Amanda Conner. They will be joined by editors Sarah Brunstad and Wil Moss.

The new series will see Carol Danvers…
